OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan gets curfew for        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbrandishing gun at drone   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpilot                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who shot at a drone flying near  
OL,6, his home and then confronted its pilot 
OL,7, with a gun has been put under curfew   
OL,8, and ordered to pay #3,000 compensation.
OL,10,FMichael Edwards, 72, was arrested in   
OL,11,FAugust after confronting estate agent  
OL,12,Fvideographer Daine Gooden in           
OL,13,FCirencester, Gloucestershire.          
OL,15,FVideo footage shows Edwards walking up 
OL,16,Fto Mr Gooden with a black airgun.      
OL,18,FAt Gloucester Crown Court he received a
OL,19,F12-month community order and was placed
OL,20,Funder curfew for four months.          
